`cfc_toLinearFunctional_bound`.-/
lemma cfc_variation_toComplexMeasure_bounded (x y : H) :
    (cfc_toComplexMeasure ha x y).variation Set.univ ≤ ‖x‖ₑ * ‖y‖ₑ := by
  rw [cfc_toComplexMeasure, ComplexRMK.variation_rieszMeasure_univ]
  apply (ENNReal.coe_le_coe.mpr (ContinuousLinearMap.nnnorm_comp_le _ _)).trans
  rw [ENNReal.coe_mul]
  simp only [ZeroAtInftyContinuousMap.ContinuousMap.nnnorm_liftZeroAtInftyCLE_symm,
    ContinuousLinearMap.nnnorm_toContinuousLinearMap, ENNReal.coe_one, mul_one]
  exact_mod_cast cfc_toLinearFunctional_bound ha x y
```
